# Keep the build context small and never leak host artifacts/secrets.
# NOTE: all package.json + source stay in context so `pnpm install
# --frozen-lockfile` matches the workspace lockfile (incl. apps/mobile);
# the runner stage copies only the web standalone bundle, so mobile deps
# never reach the runtime image.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
.git
.github
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example
**/*.log
**/coverage
**/.DS_Store
apps/web/e2e
apps/web/playwright-report
apps/web/test-results
graphify-out
